### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Tools
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tools

### Tool Details
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tools/execute_shell

### Policy
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/policy/support-agent
X-API-Key: dev-key

### Direct Decision
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/call
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: dev-key

{
  "agent_id": "support-agent",
  "tool_name": "search_kb",
  "arguments": {
    "query": "payment failures after release",
    "top_k": 2
  },
  "provider": "generic"
}

### Provider-Shaped Decision
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/decide
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: dev-key

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "payload": {
    "agent_id": "support-agent",
    "tool_call": {
      "name": "draft_reply",
      "arguments": {
        "ticket_id": "TK-1042",
        "customer_name": "Acme Health",
        "summary": "Payments failing for EU customers after release 2.8.1",
        "next_steps": [
          "Investigating gateway health",
          "Escalated to on-call"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}

